41, 136.7456, 137.9062, 138.4988, 139.0328, 138.3431, 139.2309, 139.9043, 140.2028, 139.9206, 140.95, 140.2372, 140.3829, 141.2724, 141.0433, 141.3203, 140.867, 140.4312, 140.5954, 140.6275, 140.8436, 140.7862, 140.4276, 140.6162, 140.8627, 141.2884, 141.7027, 141.6868, 142.2547, 142.6035, 143.1018, 143.3128, 142.797, 143.2994, 142.6495, 142.9795, 142.6465, 143.3375, 142.9292, 143.7799, 142.7086, 142.2942, 142.4657, 142.4148, 142.3655, 142.8561, 143.8383, 144.6685, 143.5206, 144.0682, 143.8459, 143.4508, 143.9195, 142.9724, 143.397, 142.8081, 142.8353, 141.9907, 142.3254, 142.3106, 142.1944, 142.0368, 140.5896, 140.5991, 140.9691, 141.0242, 140.9055, 140.7595, 140.9085, 141.9564, 141.4293, 140.7563, 141.7764, 141.6678, 141.43, 142.1466, 141.4978, 141.6328, 141.8475, 141.8314, 141.1252, 141.0305, 141.1958, 142.019, 141.4241, 141.2317, 140.7872, 140.0117, 140.3376, 139.9989, 139.3387, 138.7419, 138.9788, 139.18, 138.9427, 139.077, 139.0378, 138.5009, 138.689, 138.6705, 138.3589, 138.3688, 137.915, 137.6072, 137.6928, 137.481, 138.3345, 138.5546, 137.4562, 137.9155, 138.016, 138.787, 137.8711, 138.3074, 137.9032, 137.6504, 137.824, 137.2671, 136.6893, 137.1647, 137.6759, 138.5265, 138.5963, 138.8277, 138.3542, 138.9313, 139.403, 141.5938, 141.1194, 140.6426, 140.9787, 141.3667, 141.6337, 141.295, 142.4907, 141.7913, 141.2503, 141.2587, 140.6582, 141.0226, 141.4127, 141.1525, 141.4664, 142.2796, 142.3382, 141.2535, 141.0826, 142.389, 141.2613, 141.9229, 142.0504, 142.2618, 142.438, 143.0238, 142.0027, 141.1742, 141.197, 141.6811, 141.3435, 141.6394, 139.8202, 139.2423, 140.597, 140.34, 141.3999, 140.6268, 140.7187, 140.6092, 141.0567, 142.0802, 141.6105, 141.1625, 140.3326, 140.9175, 141.3433, 140.6085, 140.3491, 140.3727, 140.3538, 139.8099, 139.5236, 139.2305, 139.6654, 139.3603, 139.3408, 138.8434, 138.6995, 139.4778, 138.6947, 138.6162, 138.5597, 139.0072, 138.5169, 138.8898, 138.8568, 139.1615, 139.6464, 138.2503, 137.202, 138.1912, 137.1681, 138.1397, 138.3515, 137.8393, 137.3564, 138.3624, 139.0513, 139.5678, 139.1946, 139.1218, 139.0827, 138.967, 137.9445, 137.784, 137.8002, 138.5871, 138.7878, 139.0995, 138.3371, 137.9079, 138.41, 138.1833, 138.1516, 137.5076, 137.1778, 137.6704, 137.111, 136.9057, 136.4333, 136.2657, 136.1095, 136.3499, 136.736, 136.6621, 136.5779, 136.4235, 137.3476, 137.3191, 136.9273, 137.7344, 137.6061, 137.7136, 137.5693, 137.353, 137.5224, 137.6619, 137.6249, 138.1726, 136.8959, 136.8749, 136.9748, 137.3573, 137.87, 137.942, 138.03, 138.7877, 138.5537, 138.0406, 138.1589, 138.2482, 138.1409, 138.476, 137.6951, 136.8341, 136.4446, 136.5565, 136.9795, 136.1308, 137.361, 137.4069], "summary_html": "<h1>盈余惊喜（PEAD/SUE）→ 商品库存季节性意外</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>原研报是 A 股 PEAD（Post-Earnings Announcement Drift，盈余公告后漂移）策略：盈余惊喜 = 实际盈余 − 预期盈余；正向超预期的股票在公告日后股价持续向上漂移（\"净利润断层\"+涨幅 确认）。商品期货无财报与分析师预期，本复现把\"盈余惊喜\"迁移为<strong>基本面季节性意外（SUE）</strong>：</p>\n<ul><li><strong>预期 = 季节基准</strong>。商品库存/仓单/利润有强季节性（农产品收获季、燃料冬储等），用</li>\n</ul>  同一日历位置的去年同日值 <code>x.shift(252)</code> 作为\"市场预期\"。\n<ul><li><strong>意外（surprise） = 当前值 − 季节基准</strong>，再用过去 surprise 的滚动标准差<strong>标准化</strong>得到</li>\n</ul>  SUE（Standardized Unexpected），使其衡量\"未预期程度\"而非单纯 YoY 水平——这是区别于\n<p>已有\"库存农历同比\"因子的关键。</p>\n<ul><li><strong>PEAD 漂移方向</strong>：库存/仓单<strong>低于</strong>季节预期（负意外）= 供给偏紧 = 看多；利润<strong>高于</strong></li>\n</ul>  季节预期（正意外）= 看多。漂移持续 → 用较长 hold（21 天）让信号持续生效。\n<p>为什么能赚钱：与原文行为金融解释同源——投资者对基本面季节性意外反应不足（有限注意力）， 供需信息逐步定价，价格沿意外方向漂移。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.88</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>4.4%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>5.0%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-9.6%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.04</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3446</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.08</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>-0.37</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>0.91 / 1.4</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>0.71</td><td>1.94</td><td>0.91</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.04</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.24</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.05</span></td><td>1.43</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.12</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.36</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.04</span></td><td>0.93</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.28</span></td><td>0.15</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-1.0</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>inventory_21</code></td><td>库存(21日)</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>receipt</code></td><td>仓单</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>profit</code></td><td>利润</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 21 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 21 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3448</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>77.1%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>35.6</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p>对每个基本面变量 x ∈ {inventory, receipt, profit}（按 sym 前向填充）：</p>\n<p>surprise_{i,t} = x_{i,t} - x_{i,t-252} SUE_{i,t}      = surprise_{i,t} / ( std_252(surprise_{i,·}) + ε )</p>\n<p>截面排名 r_{i,t} = rank_t(SUE_{i,t}) ∈ [0,1]，方向化后等权组合：</p>\n<p>dir_combo_{i,t} = (2/3) · [ (0.5 - r_inv) + (0.5 - r_rcpt) + (r_prof - 0.5) ]</p>\n<p>（库存/仓单取 0.5−r 使低意外→做多；利润取 r−0.5 使高意外→做多。）</p>\n<p>仓位：pos = rebalance_hold( vol_target_scale(dir, 0.15), hold=21 )。</p>\n<p>PEAD 事件（\"净利润断层\"迁移）：|SUE_inv| &gt; 1.5 触发事件，方向持有 21 天。</p>\n<ul><li>x_{i,t-252}：去年同日季节基准（1 年≈252 交易日）；std_252：surprise 滚动标准差；ε=1e-8。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>迭代记录</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>R1</strong>（baseline）：三类 SUE（库存/仓单/利润）+ 等权 combo（10/21/42 hold）+ PEAD 事件</li>\n</ul>  变体。best <code>combo_h21_ts</code> = 1.23，所有 gate 通过，ts_ic 正、冗余 new_signal。\n<ul><li><strong>R2</strong>：加 <code>sym_rolling_ic_gate(252)</code> 滚动 IC 过滤弱品种。gated 变体（0.88-0.91）反而低于</li>\n</ul>  ungated combo——信号在品种间普遍有效，过滤损失好品种，best 维持 1.23。\n<ul><li><strong>R3</strong>：加 supply-only combo（库存+仓单，剔除噪声大的利润）。<code>supply_h21_ts</code> 1.06，略低于</li>\n</ul>  含利润的完整 combo；确认三因子等权 combo 最稳。decision=skip（≥3 轮、全 gate 通过）。\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>：日频（<code>comm_data/daily/kline_daynight_all.parquet</code>）。</li>\n<li><strong>字段依赖</strong>：<code>inventory_21/inventory_lp</code>、<code>receipt</code>、<code>profit</code>（非空率 72-85%）。</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>：58 个有基本面数据的商品；持仓周期 21 天。</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>：(1) 换手 2.52 偏高，对成本敏感；(2) 2024 年小幅为负，纯基本面策略在</li>\n</ul>  无明显季节意外的年份信号弱；(3) 需 ≥1 年历史才能计算季节基准（首年为热身期）。\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.94s</li>\n</ul>"}